                            <comment id="63230" author="simmonsja" created="Tue, 30 Jul 2013 12:08:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All patches have been landed. Peter can you close this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="63043" author="simmonsja" created="Fri, 26 Jul 2013 15:24:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This list is more what is needed to have proper behavior on 3.9 kernels. True the fixes for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3486&quot; title=&quot;LBUG when exporting Lustre 2.4 via NFS on SLES11SP2: ll_dops_init: ASSERTION( de-&amp;gt;d_op == &amp;amp;ll_d_ops ) failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3486&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3486&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3581&quot; title=&quot;Recurrence of LU-3020: Lustre returns EINTR during writes when SA_RESTART is set &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3581&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3581&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; are needed in a more broad scope. In that case we really only have two patches left, both for this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="63040" author="bogl" created="Fri, 26 Jul 2013 15:08:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I wonder why you list &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7002&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7002&lt;/a&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3581&quot; title=&quot;Recurrence of LU-3020: Lustre returns EINTR during writes when SA_RESTART is set &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3581&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3581&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; here.  This doesn&apos;t seem 3.9 specific.  While I agree the fix is needed I don&apos;t see what makes it more important for 3.9 than for earlier kernels.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="63037" author="simmonsja" created="Fri, 26 Jul 2013 14:41:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patches needed for Linux 3.9 are now:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6797&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6797&lt;/a&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3486&quot; title=&quot;LBUG when exporting Lustre 2.4 via NFS on SLES11SP2: ll_dops_init: ASSERTION( de-&amp;gt;d_op == &amp;amp;ll_d_ops ) failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3486&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3486&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (NFS related)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7002&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7002&lt;/a&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3581&quot; title=&quot;Recurrence of LU-3020: Lustre returns EINTR during writes when SA_RESTART is set &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3581&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3581&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (NFS related)&lt;br/&gt;
